#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an9.34:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, enters and remains in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "

msgctxt "an9.34:9.2"
msgid "Tassa ce, āvuso, bhikkhuno iminā vihārena viharato ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti, svassa hoti ābādho. "
msgstr "While a mendicant is in such a meditation, should perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset them, that’s an affliction for them. "

msgctxt "an9.34:9.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya; "
msgstr "Suppose a happy person were to experience pain; that would be an affliction for them. "

msgctxt "an9.34:9.4"
msgid "evamevassa te ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa hoti ābādho. "
msgstr "In the same way, should perceptions and attentions accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset them, that’s an affliction for them. "

msgctxt "an9.34:9.5"
msgid "Yo kho panāvuso, ābādho dukkhametaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā. "
msgstr "And affliction has been called suffering by the Buddha. "

msgctxt "an9.34:9.6"
msgid "Imināpi kho etaṃ, āvuso, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sukhaṃ nibbānaṃ. (8) "
msgstr "That too is a way to understand how extinguishment is bliss. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.418, sc10
msgctxt "an9.34:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā parikkhīṇā honti. (9) "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements come to an end. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an9.34:11.1"
msgid "Imināpi kho etaṃ, āvuso, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sukhaṃ nibbānan”ti. "
msgstr "That too is a way to understand how extinguishment is bliss.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.34:11.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

